					                <div class="avatar"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/be4353be54885e1c227915d4077f8f80?s=40&amp;d=retro&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' /></div>
	                        
	
